message: The Horry County Sheriff's Office hosted a community event to raise awareness about human trafficking and how the public could help to combat it. #LE #makingadifference

data.description: The Horry County Sheriff's Office and the South Carolina Coastal Region Task Force on Human Trafficking will host a public meeting this morning to educate the community about how they can get involved to end human trafficking on the Grand Strand.
data.title: Horry County law enforcement agencies work to educate the community about human trafficking
